                     <interp inst="t18340904-60-person428" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , warehouseman, Old Change, and Mrs. Ramsden, wife of 
               <persName id="t18340904-60-person429">
                  Thomas 
                  Ramsden
               <interp inst="t18340904-60-person429" type="surname" value="Ramsden"></interp>
