                     <interp inst="t18340904-60-person429" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , colour-maker, Whitechapel, gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18340904-60-verdict338" type="verdictDescription">
